metadata.title: Taygate WiFi Range Extender, Up to 2640sq.ft WiFi Extender, 2.4G High Speed Wireless WiFi Repeater with Integrated Antennas Ethernet Port, 360° Full WiFi Coverage, Supports Repeater/AP/WPS, White
features: 【Extend WiFi Signal to Dead Zone】- Stable WiFi Signal Booster wireless internet amplifier full coverage, eliminate home WiFi dead zones. You will now be able to surf the internet, watch videos, play games, and video chat anywhere in your home without worry about getting stuck or dropping the Internet(US Plug).

【Supports 2 Working Modes】- Wi-Fi Extender has 2 Ethernet Ports with Repeater/AP, can easily turn your wired Internet connection into a wireless access point. It can also function as a wireless adapter to connect any Ethernetenabled wired devices, like Blu-ray player, game console, desktop or smart TV. Which can easily meet different needs.

【Wide Compatibility】- The Range Extender is compatible with all Wi-Fi-enabled devices and WiFi routers or WiFi Access Points. All Wi-Fi extenders are designed to increase or improve Wi-Fi coverage, not to directly increase speed.
【Quick and Easy Setup】- It can easily extend the wireless coverage by pressing One-touch WPS Button on Your Existing Router. On almost any devices, including Windows/Android/iOS mobile platforms.

【Safe Network Access】- This Wifi Booster can maximize the network security, ensure your network safety, prevent others stealing your net, protect your important data and avoid the interference and privacy problems of Wi-Fi. Please contact us freely if you need any further assistance.
description: Quick and Easy Installation One button operation, Simply plug and play! The WiFi Range Extender has a WPS button, you can set it up by simply pressing the WPS button! You can also set up via log in the website on any mobile devices. The specific installation method is detailed in the manual. Discrete Wall Plug Design Plug into a wall outlet for a sleek solution that extends your router's range and stays out of sight. Universally Compatible This Wi-Fi signal booster can easily expand the wireless coverage by press the WPS button on your original router and this repeater, only takes a few seconds. Very easy to set up. Say Goodbye to WiFi Dead Zones Help you keep mobile devices, media players and computers connected to Wi-Fi with a reliable connection and expanded coverage in every corner of your home. Extender has small size with better performance, extending wifi coverage, say goodbye to dead zones, ideal for your bedroom, floors, restroom etc. Package includes 1x Wifi Repeater 1 x User Manual Installation Guide Q: Can I plug it in to a 220 voltage wall outlet? A: Yes, the voltage of the repeater is 110-230V. Q: Which router is compatible? A: It can be used as long as there is a wireless signal. Q: Does this plug into a standard outlet? A: Yes, it does. Q: Will this make my bad signal better? A: The repeater can only enlarge the distance of the WiFi signal, but can not enhance the speed of the WiFi signal.
